		<title>Smoldering multiple myeloma: What it is, how it progresses and the latest research</title>
		<link>https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/discussion/smoldering-multiple-myeloma-what-it-is-how-it-progresses-and-the-latest-research/</link>
		
